1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/* 	$OpenBSD: modload.c,v 1.38 2003/03/13 09:09:26 deraadt Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: modload.c,v 1.30 2001/11/08 15:33:15 christos Exp $	*/

/*
